                            <comment id="13068897" author="vivekp" created="Thu, 21 Jul 2011 11:53:26 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks like a change in behaviour introduced due to the parser changes. In Pig 0.8 , &quot;describe ; &quot; would show the describe of the last alias&lt;br/&gt;
rather than NullPointerException. This is done through;&lt;br/&gt;
 alias = mPigServer.getPigContext().getLastAlias(); , but in 0.9, the last alias is not captured in Pig Context.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Attaching an initial patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
